==English==

==={{acronym}}===
'''LAN'''  (''plural:'' '''[[LANs]]''')
# ''(Computers)'' [[acronym]] for "'''Local Area Network'''", as contrasted with a '''[[WAN]]''', or ''Wide Area Network''.  An interconnection of computers that are in relatively close proximity to each other, such as within a building.
#: ''A LAN connects all of the computers in our office.''

#: ''A LAN can also be consisted with gaming terms e.g LAN party. This consists of groups of people bring computers, connecting them to enjoy with friends over a friendly round of counter-strike. This can also happen in places such as an internet Cafe''

